{
  "texts": [
    "Following this, bias levels of LLMs are quantified by measuring toxicity values across different groups.",
    "Ultimately, value alignment is appraised by gauging LLMs' rejection of content that contradicts human values.",
    "• FACTOR (Muhlgay et al, 2023).",
    "The FACTOR dataset is divided into Wiki-FACTOR and News-FACTOR, distinguished by their respective data sources.",
    "The dataset consists of 4,030 English samples, with 2,994 in Wiki-FACTOR and 1,036 in News-FACTOR."
  ]
}